English:
This is the Bulgarian translation of "The not so short introduction to LaTeX2e" 
by Tobias Oetiker (version 4.12, April,2003).
(C) 2005 for this translation by Stefka Karakoleva: 
         e-mail:skarakoleva@ru.acad.bg 
Address: RU "Agel Kanchev" 
         8 Studentska str.
         7017, Rousse
         Bulgaria

Public domain.

Contents:
lshort-bg.dvi                DVI file
lshort-bg.ps                 PostScript file 
lshort-bg-book.ps            PostScript file for printing A5 booklet
lshort-bg.pdf                PDF version built by pdflatex
src                          Тhis subdirectory contains the LaTeX2e 
                             document sources.

